# Shared .dockerignore for both backend and frontend image builds (context = repo root).
**/.git
**/.github
**/.githooks
**/node_modules
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/.pytest_cache
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/coverage
**/.vscode
**/.idea
# Repo docs / test artifacts not needed in images
docs
test_reports
memory
data/exports
**/*.md
!frontend/public/**
CCMS-SDD.docx
